name: Entry to the Universe
description: "Entry to the Universe". This pice is part of a series of 20 surreal generative artworks of abstract pointillism aiming to reflect the surreal visuals of a dreamlike hallucinatory state of mind where the distinction between reality and dreams is blurred (a.k.a. Oneirophrenia). Charcteristics: 5400 x 4200 pixels at 320 DPI.
